data.title: Wiktionary, the free dictionary
data.text:
This is the main category of the Fula language.

It is spoken in Niger, Nigeria, Benin, Burkina Faso, Cameroon, the Central African Republic, Chad, the Gambia, Guinea, Guinea-Bissau, Mali, Mauritania, Senegal, Sierra Leone, and Togo.
